expect someone to mock your zealotry. So it goes for the two dozen
dedicated souls who are waiting for the next saga in the Star Wars
series, Episode 1: The Phantom Menace, at the makeshift campground
outside Mann's Chinese Theater in Hollywood, Calif. (Houck, Palm
Beach Post) MOVED MONDAY.
