Railroad (Ferrocarril Transandino) offers a roof-top ride across
Ecuador from Riobaba to Guayaquil. The huddled masses atop the
train hang on for dear life - but enjoy some fabulous vistas.
(Schemmel, Atlanta Journal-Constitution freelancer; not for use by
NYTNS clients) WITH PHOTOS.
</P>
