or morality or other Big Issues. I went solely to check out the
charmisa factor; her ``wattage,'' if you will. Does she burn
brightly enough to light up a room? Or does she unleash barely
enough amps to power an electric toothbrush? (Sturrock, Palm Beach
Post) MOVED.
</P>
