<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-29 13:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7926 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CHILDCARE-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      04-29 1630
