   NATIONAL NEWS (``a'' category)
</P>
<P>
   KIDS-SLAIN (Austin, Texas) _ The bodies of the brother and
sister, ages 2 and 3, who were found slain last week in a creek
north of Austin are buried in an Austin cemetery. Meanwhile, their
mother, 22-year-old Tina Marie Cornelius, is being questioned by
investigators. By JAMIE STOCKWELL.
</P>
<P>
   KID-INSURANCE (Austin, Texas) _ The state House is expected to
consider a plan to increase insurance coverage for Texas children.
By JOHN GONZALEZ.
