atmosphere of panic over school safety. By Robert D. McFadden.
</P>
<P>
   SCI-FROG-WARNING (Undated) _ Frogs with multiple limbs and other
deformities have been reported more and more often in recent years,
feeding worries that the frogs are bellwethers of some looming
environmental apocalypse. Two new studies reported in the journal
Science tomorrow conclude that at least some of the frog
deformities are the result of natural parasites in the wild. By
Carol Kaesuk Yoon.
</P>
<P>
   SCI-MARS-TECTONICS (Undated) _ A telling magnetic pattern in the
ancient surface of Mars appears to show that the planet in an early
epoch churned with internal heat, shifting sections of the crust
and other powerful forces remarkably like the geology of Earth
today, scientists reported. By John Noble Wilford.
</P>
