<HEADLINE>
BIG-TOP KALEIDOSCAPE TAKES A CUE FROM `OTHER' CIRCUSES
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Editors: Includes L.A.-area schedule box at bottom) 
By GLENN WHIPP  
 c.1999 Los AN'&AMP;kV+V.HQ%1e
<TEXT>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
