   YUGOSLAVIA-KOSOVO CONFLICT
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-CONGRESS _ WASHINGTON _ The House's refusal to support
the NATO air war reverberated around Capitol Hill and the White
House on Thursday, even as the House Appropriations Committee
prepared to double President Clinton's military spending request.
(Malone, Cox News Service). 20.
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-REFUGEES _ KUKES, Albania _ the latest developments from
this nation bordering the embattled Yugoslav province of Kosovo as
refugees from there continue pour over into packed camps.
Developing. (Kunstel, Cox News Service).
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-TROOPS _ TIRANA, Albania _ The mood of the U.S. Army
troops that would likely make up the strikeforce for any ground
troops that would be sent into the embattled Yugoslav province of
Kosovo. The men and women of Task Force Hawk are showing a little
frustration as the military campaign gets stretched out. And
talking to several from the Apache unit, including the chaplain
they admit to frustration as the world sees the vaunted weapon as
less than perfect. Developing. (Albright, Cox News Service).
</P>
