<P>
   MISSING-MOM-FOUND _ AUSTIN, Texas _ Tina Marie Cornelius'
children were buried Thursday as investigators continued to
interrogate her. Charges were possible Thursday afternoon.
Meanwhile, we get detail on how she spent her time in Corpus
Christi after meeting a man while waiting in line for a carnival
ride. We also believe she was caught after applying for a welfare
card using her real name. They arrested and held her on hot check
charges. You don't go writing hot checks down in Corpus Christi.
(Spencer, Austin American-Statesman)
</P>
