computers, safety and other classroom uses may be starting to
dwindle. The overall funding for the lottery's primary programs _
Hope Scholarships and pre-kindergarten programs _ are not thought
to be in jeopardy. (Mantius, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
MOVED.
</P>
