<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-29 18:01 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8382 &Cx1f; tab-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NYTBOOK-FRIEND-NYTSF     04-29 1127
