the humiliation of the House refusing to support the US role in
Kosovo, endures the embarrassment of a wayward NATO missile
slamming into Bulgaria and the uncertain prospect of the Rev. Jesse
Jackson's arrival in Yugoslavia on an unauthorized peace mission.
By Bob Hohler. 1200 words.
