fans for their home opener. With new ownership and management,
things seem to be looking up for the oft-struggling franchise. But
can the fan support be expected to continue? And what about Major
League Soccer? They don't even consider Atlanta a possibility for
expansion. (Parker, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 20-25. MOVED
